data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Move into the Liberty Square neighborhood! Super cute 3 bedroom 2 bath house with 2 car garage with a large fenced in back yard! This great house has a Large great room with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Primary bedroom has a large walk in closet and a bathroom with double sinks, soaking tub and stand up shower. Laminate and tile floors through out. Great location!
